reviewText: I've received the guide on time and well packaged. The course in itself was not as informative as I would have expected.

I gave a 5-star rating not so much for the item, but for the seller.  I had ordered the incorrect guide.  I wanted the guide to Italy Wines but mistakenly ordered the guide to France wines.  The seller responded timely, and was very cooperative,  to my request to return the item.
